.TH MNEMOSYNE-WIKI-PRUNE 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne wiki-prune \- Plan stale wiki/graph reconciliation without deleting evidence.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne wiki-prune\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Plan stale wiki/graph reconciliation without deleting evidence.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-wiki\-root\fR
LLM Wiki root (default: ~/mnemosyne/wiki)
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR
KnowledgeGraph DB path
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-lock\-timeout\fR
Seconds to wait for the wiki write lock on write commands
.TP
\fB\-\-apply\-tombstones\fR
Write tombstone records without deleting pages or graph facts
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
